Functionality
  Generate Survey
    Create questions
      Matrix, multiple choice and text entry
      Can be done from a template
    Organize questions
      Display logic, hide and show question based on answer to previous
    Survey should be saved/stored and editable
  Distribute Survey
    Allow outside users to take the survey
    Printable
    Compressed into public web link for distribution
  Collecting Data
    Recieve responses
    Store in correct hierachy in the database
  Query Data
    User Interface that allows for performing SQL queries
      Can provide metrics for Count, Average, Sum
      Breakout data by demographic information
      Need to be able to query multiple tables
  Generate Report
    Produce a printable report of select summary data or queries
